# 🚨 Helmet Violation Detection System

A real-time helmet violation detection system built using **YOLOv8**, **Streamlit**, and **PaddleOCR**.

This app detects:
- Motorcyclists **without helmets** within a defined zone
- Automatically captures and **logs number plates** of violators

---

## 🔧 Features

- 🎥 **Live Detection** via Webcam or Uploaded Video  
- 🧠 **YOLOv8** for detecting helmets and number plates  
- 🔤 **PaddleOCR** for number plate recognition  
- 🗺️ Polygonal **Zone-based detection**  
- 📝 Fine Logging:
  - Vehicle number  
  - Date and Time  
  - Snapshot of number plate  
- 📁 Export fines as CSV  
- 📸 Image preview of captured plates  

---

## 🖥️ Interface (Streamlit)

- **Sidebar**: View Violation History  
- **Main View**:
  - Live/resumed video feed  
  - Real-time fine log table  
  - Number plate image gallery  
  - Download fine log as CSV  

---

## 🧰 Installation

> Make sure **Python 3.8+** is installed.

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/helmet-fine-detection.git
cd helmet-fine-detection
